{"title":"La structure de donn\u00e9es","headline":"Manipuler le fichier models.php ","author":"root","article":"<p class=\"p1\">L&rsquo;admin du site se construit avec des &laquo;&nbsp;blocks&nbsp;&raquo; qui sont simplement des tableaux en PHP. Il est donc tr&egrave;s facile d&rsquo;ajouter un champ ou un &eacute;diteur wysiwyg dans l&rsquo;administration du site. Le contenu du champ pourra &ecirc;tre r&eacute;cup&eacute;r&eacute; ais&eacute;ment sur le site.<\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>$swcnt_tree<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Le tableau $swcnt_tree contient les pages de l&rsquo;espace &laquo;&nbsp;Editeur&nbsp;&raquo;. Vous pouvez cr&eacute;er facilement l&rsquo;administration d&rsquo;une page d&rsquo;accueil, du footer.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Ajouter ce tableau permet de cr&eacute;er la page Popol dans l&rsquo;admin.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">$swcnt_tree[&lsquo;popol&rsquo;]&nbsp;=&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;sw_title&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&lsquo;Page de Popol&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;sw_blocks&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">);<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Le &laquo;&nbsp;block&nbsp;&raquo; suivant est utilis&eacute; pour g&eacute;rer la page d&rsquo;infos du site. Chaque block est un champ dans la DB.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Les diff&eacute;rents types de champs sont :<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">input_txt<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">textarea<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">htmlarea -&gt; &eacute;diteur wysiwyg summernote<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">blogarea -&gt; &eacute;diteur wysiwyg tinymce<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">select<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">checkbox<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">tags<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">picture -&gt; un bouton pour t&eacute;l&eacute;charger une photo.<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">list -&gt; permet de cr&eacute;er une sous-liste de champs en tableau. Pratique pour cr&eacute;er un album photos ou la navigation du site.<\/span><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><em>Exemple:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">$swcnt_tree[&lsquo;siteinfos&rsquo;]&nbsp;=&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;sw_title&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;site&nbsp;infos&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;sw_blocks&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;title&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;_(&lsquo;Site&nbsp;title&rsquo;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;Mon&nbsp;site&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;baseline&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;_(&lsquo;Site&nbsp;baseline&rsquo;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;Un&nbsp;site&nbsp;cool&nbsp;pour&nbsp;tout&nbsp;le&nbsp;monde&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;site_url&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;_(&lsquo;Site&nbsp;URL&rsquo;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;http:\/\/mysite.com&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;navigation&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;Navigation&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;list&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;submenu&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;name&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;_(&lsquo;Page&nbsp;name&rsquo;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;Mon&nbsp;page&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;url&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;_(&lsquo;URL&rsquo;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;mapage&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;twitter&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;Profil&nbsp;twitter&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;http:\/\/twitter.com\/swalize&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;facebook&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;label&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;Profil&nbsp;facebook&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;type&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;input_txt&rsquo;,<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&rsquo;placeholder&rsquo;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&rsquo;http:\/\/facebook.com\/swalize&rsquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">);<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>$swcnt_blog, $swcnt_portfolio, $swcnt_catalog<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Il s&rsquo;agit de la structure des page d&rsquo;articles, de produits ou de portfolio. Customisable avec les m&ecirc;mes champs que le $swcnt_tree. Attention, certains champs sont utiles :&laquo;&nbsp;title,pubdate,category&nbsp;&raquo;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>$swcnt_form<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Utiles pour stocker des formulaires utilis&eacute;s par les plugins ou le site. Par exemple :<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">$swcnt_form[&lsquo;contactform&rsquo;] = array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">'firstname' =&gt; array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'label' =&gt; 'Firstname',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'type' =&gt; 'input_txt',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'required'<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; <\/span>=&gt; 'Please enter your name.'<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p5\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">'lastname' =&gt; array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'label' =&gt; 'Lastname',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'type' =&gt; 'input_txt',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'required'<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; <\/span>=&gt; 'Please enter your name.'<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p5\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">'email' =&gt; array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'label' =&gt; 'Email Adress',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'type' =&gt; 'input_txt',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'required'<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; <\/span>=&gt; 'Please enter your email address.'<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">),<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">'message' =&gt; array(<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'label' =&gt; 'Message',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'type' =&gt; 'textarea',<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span>'required'<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; <\/span>=&gt; 'Please enter your message.'<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">);<\/span><\/p>","pubdate":"2016-02-13 18:47:35"}